76
00:03:34,924 --> 00:03:36,378
Entre ali.

77
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:37,875
Eu estou indo.

78
00:03:37,878 --> 00:03:39,077
Entre já.

79
00:03:55,986 --> 00:04:00,718
-  Por: RedQueen -

80
00:04:02,671 --> 00:04:04,170
Sente-se.

81
00:04:08,171 --> 00:04:09,503
Lugar legal.

82
